title: And just like that...we're Dak!
description:
Field Yates tells Mina that Dak Prescott's new contract is quite possibly the best deal ever signed by a player in NFL history. Then they look at the eight teams last place teams and discuss ways they can improve. Should the Falcons, Jets, Broncos, and Lions all be targeting a quarterback in the first round of the draft. Will Jimmy G be the 49ers starter in Week 1?
